{"word":"αἱρετέος","slug":"αἱρετέος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>αἱρετέος</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:verbal Adjective'>verb. <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a></a> of <a href='S:αἱρέω'><el>αἱρέω</el></a>,\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>to be taken, desirable</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><el>αἱρετέον</el>, <i>one must choose</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}